<dl id="n22081c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n22" href="#n22081c">N22 (VI.B.17)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n22all.htm#n22081c"> 81(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Fra Giordano</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">To the congregation (of the Holy Office) &ldquo;there were read eight heretical propositions, taken from the works of Fra Giordano Bruno of Nola, apostate of the order of Preaching Friars, imprisoned in the prison of the Holy Office, and from the process against him, by the Reverend Fathers Commissario and Bellarmino. <small> J. Lewis McIntyre, <a name="BRUNO" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#BRUNO"><cite title="source">Giordano Bruno</cite></a> (1903) 88</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
